  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 15.020000457763672,
      "text": "Ooh, baby, I think that you need a contemplative restart in your mind",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 28.260000228881836,
      "text": "Like a redesign, there's no crime in wanting better than you see",
      "start": 15.859999656677246
    },
    {
      "end": 36.70000076293945,
      "text": "Ooh, baby, I know you, it's you",
      "start": 28.260000228881836
    },
    {
      "end": 44.97999954223633,
      "text": "All I know is you're just frozen",
      "start": 36.70000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 52.220001220703125,
      "text": "Frozen inside, girl, just blazing",
      "start": 48.2599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 59.52000045776367,
      "text": "Always the fire from the night, you're just frozen",
      "start": 52.220001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 71.0999984741211,
      "text": "Ooh, every time you talk about the things that make you lose",
      "start": 63.060001373291016
    },
    {
      "end": 74,
      "text": "Inside, girl, you're frozen",
      "start": 71.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 82.86000061035156,
      "text": "In the spectacular view of your defeat",
      "start": 76.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 88.0199966430664,
      "text": "But there's still hope in here, and I promise you",
      "start": 83.30000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 94.63999938964844,
      "text": "I know the night gets darker then it gets light quicker",
      "start": 89.5999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 98.9000015258789,
      "text": "And the coldest of the coldest when it comes to your damn right",
      "start": 94.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 105.31999969482422,
      "text": "Just before the whole entire room, there's a sun wave",
      "start": 98.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 110.95999908447266,
      "text": "Someway we'll make it through this and not be frozen",
      "start": 105.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 120.04000091552734,
      "text": "And someday I won't be frozen",
      "start": 115.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 125.5,
      "text": "In the night, in the light, in the everything that makes me right",
      "start": 120.04000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 129.63999938964844,
      "text": "I can't find my words",
      "start": 125.5
    },
    {
      "end": 136.72000122070312,
      "text": "When you do it all night, it infections my energy",
      "start": 129.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 139.82000732421875,
      "text": "In the swarm of all, you're frozen",
      "start": 136.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 147.24000549316406,
      "text": "I know, can't let the right one in, you're blazing",
      "start": 140.9600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 154.44000244140625,
      "text": "With all that fire in you, baby, you're frozen",
      "start": 148.24000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 162.8800048828125,
      "text": "We'll get melt, ice down around you",
      "start": 157.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 168.0800018310547,
      "text": "I hope so too, you'll see",
      "start": 162.8800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 177.94000244140625,
      "text": "I know, you think it's all on shot",
      "start": 172.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 183.32000732421875,
      "text": "But maybe there's more than what you think you got",
      "start": 177.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 190.32000732421875,
      "text": "Seems the money's on the table, baby, I'm betting us",
      "start": 185.52000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 198.66000366210938,
      "text": "Seems the money's on the table, baby, don't bet on us, you're frozen",
      "start": 192.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 206.0800018310547,
      "text": "I know, you're freezing",
      "start": 198.8000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 212.52000427246094,
      "text": "With all the fire that's loving you season",
      "start": 206.89999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 217.6199951171875,
      "text": "I wish you could get high again",
      "start": 212.52000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 223.39999389648438,
      "text": "Maybe bring our life up to a light so we can",
